<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BRAVIA - Header Padding</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .app {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        /* ==============================================
                THE HEADER - PADDING IS SET RIGHT HERE
                ============================================== */
        .site-header {
            background: #0b0b0b;      /* Dark background */
            color: #f0f0f0;
            
            /* ★ THIS IS THE HEADER PADDING YOU ASKED FOR ★ */
            padding: 20px 48px;        
            
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;          /* Wraps items on small screens */
            gap: 15px 30px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
        }

        /* Logo / Brand */
        .brand {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        /* ==============================================
                ★ TOP MENU ITEMS ★
                NOTICE: "Nos univers" has been moved to the VERY END 
                (just before the closing </nav> tag) to prove it moves!
                ============================================== */
        .main-nav {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px 25px;
        }

        .main-nav a {
            color: #d0d0d0;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            padding-bottom: 4px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
            transition: 0.2s;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .main-nav a:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
            border-bottom-color: #888;
        }

        /* Right side actions (Shopping & Gemini) */
        .header-actions {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .header-actions a {
            color: #d0d0d0;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .header-actions a:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .gemini-badge {
            background: #2a2a2a;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        /* Sidebar mockup */
        .sidebar-panel {
            background: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 15px 48px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px 30px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #333;
        }
        .sidebar-panel span {
            background: white;
            padding: 4px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
        }

        /* Main content mockup */
        .main-content {
            padding: 30px 48px;
            min-height: 300px;
        }

        /* THIS IS THE SECOND "NOS UNIVERS" (in the gray content area, NOT the menu) */
        .menu-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px 25px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .menu-grid span {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #222;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 20px 48px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            color: #555;
        }

        /* Makes it look good on phones */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .site-header {
                padding: 15px 20px; /* Smaller padding for mobile */
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: stretch;
            }
            .main-nav {
                justify-content: center;
            }
            .header-actions {
                justify-content: center;
            }
            .sidebar-panel, .main-content, .footer {
                padding-left: 20px;
                padding-right: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="app">

    <!-- ==========================================
    HEADER STARTS HERE
    ========================================== -->
    <header class="site-header">

        <!-- Left: Logo -->
        <div class="brand">
            ⬛ BRAVIA
        </div>

        <!-- ==========================================
        ★★★ TOP MENU - "Nos univers" is now at the END ★★★
        Look at the bottom of this list!
        ========================================== -->
        <nav class="main-nav">
            <a href="#">Accueil</a>
            <!-- Notice "Nos univers" is MISSING from here now -->
            <a href="#">Nouveautés</a>
            <a href="#">Mode & Accessoires</a>
            <a href="#">Sport & Fitness</a>
            <a href="#">Maison & Décoration</a>
            <a href="#">Beauté</a>
            <a href="#">Électronique</a>
            <a href="#">Nos univers</a>   <!-- 👈 I MOVED IT DOWN HERE TO THE END! -->
        </nav>

        <!-- Right: Actions -->
        <div class="header-actions">
            <a href="#">🛒 Shopping</a>
            <a href="#" class="gemini-badge">✨ Ask Gemini</a>
        </div>

    </header>

    <!-- Sidebar mockup -->
    <div class="sidebar-panel">
        <span>⚙️ Theme settings</span>
        <span>Theme</span>
        <span>Custom CSS</span>
        <span style="border-left: none; background: transparent; border: none; color: #777;">Add custom styles to your entire online store.</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Main content mockup -->
    <main class="main-content">
        <div class="menu-grid">
            <span>ACCUEIL</span>
            <span>NOS UNIVERS</span> <!-- THIS IS THE ONE IN THE CONTENT AREA, NOT THE TOP MENU -->
            <span>NOUVEAUTÉS</span>
            <span>MODE & ACCESSOIRES</span>
            <span>SPORT & FITNESS</span>
            <span>MAISON & DÉCORATION</span>
            <span>BEAUTÉ</span>
            <span>ÉLECTRONIQUE</span>
        </div>
        <p style="color: #555; font-size: 1.1rem;">
            ✅ Look at the <strong>top dark menu</strong>. <br>
            ✅ <strong>"Nos univers"</strong> is now the <strong>last</strong> item (after "Électronique"). <br>
            ✅ If you want to move it back, just cut <code>&lt;a href="#"&gt;Nos univers&lt;/a&gt;</code> and paste it anywhere else inside the <strong>&lt;nav&gt;</strong> tag.
        </p>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <span>© BRAVIA</span>
        <span>Activate Windo</span>
    </footer>

</div>

</body>
</html>